	<region id="editorData">
		<node id="editorData">
			<attribute id="HowToTrigger" type="LSString" value="- Load up GustavDev/CTY_Main_A&#xD;&#xA;- Use &quot;oe MT_Start&quot;, enter the tombstone shop and go down into the Murder Tribunal&#xD;&#xA;- Use &quot;oe MT_Dolor_Assault_Cheats&quot; to get Dolor to appear at the Death Knight guarding the courtroom. He will start attacking the Death Knight and will then turn his attention to the Murder Tribunal.&#xD;&#xA;- It's best to join this combat and use &quot;killcombat&quot;, provided Dolor is still neutral to us.&#xD;&#xA;- If Dolor somehow survives the whole ordeal and the Tribunal ends up dead, he will turn on the players and say this AD on his first combat turn." />
			<attribute id="needLayout" type="bool" value="False" />
			<attribute id="nextNodeId" type="uint32" value="1" />
			<attribute id="synopsis" type="LSString" value="After killing the Murder Tribunal, Dolor turns on our party and starts attacking us." />
